    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) and cook for 5-6 min or until browned and crisped, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the mince is cooking, deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>sliced pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the pepper has started to soften</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>sticky chilli sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has started to soften, add your <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>sticky chilli sauce</strong> and cook for 2 min or until everything is coated and sticky and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>sticky chilli stir-fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/sticky-chilli-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky chilli pork stir-fry</strong> over the<strong> basmati rice</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
